<h4 style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 5px"><li>What is SeatSwappr?</li></h4>
SeatSwappr is currently an online marketplace for passengers to sell, search, buy and swap seats. Passengers may want to swap seats for many reasons, such as sitting next to family or friends, obnoxious passenger, more space, etc. SeatSwappr facilitates that swap by putting passengers in touch with each other.
 
<h4 style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 5px"><li>Can SeatSwappr issue new boarding passes?</li></h4>
Currently, SeatSwappr cannot issue new boarding passes. That is why we ask passengers to board with their original boarding passes and swap once on the plane. We hope to work with airlines to issue new boarding passes once both parties have agreed.

